                                                </p>
                                            </blockquote>

                                            <p class="author">&mdash; محسن صادقی</p>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="testimony">
                                            <blockquote>
                                                <img src="~/assets/images/person_3.jpg" alt="Image" class="img-fluid">
